a, USA.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","width":"full","padding_bottom":16}},"features_HXmJxr":{"type":"features","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-chat","icon_size":20,"title":"Need styling help?","text_font_size":"body-medium","text":"<p>Book an appointment with our virtual stylists! <a href=\"\/pages\/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact Us\"><em><strong>service@solariijewelry.com<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>","bg_color":"","color":"","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["title","loox_reviews_loox_rating_RmpBmG","loox_reviews_loox_snippets_widget_kpeXU3","price","countdown_dbJGaa","accordion_X9nqxr","variants","klarna_on_site_messaging_app_block_QyN4yT","buttons","trustz_payment_badge_rnKfx4","accordion_jHM8Nn","accordion_tMFjyA","icon_1","icon_663HJF","icon_2","icon_KMKHHa","icon_MxUb8a","features_HXmJxr"],"settings":{"product_sticky_enable":true,"variant_image_scroll":true,"show_cart_bar":true,"enable_zoom":true,"enable_video_looping":false,"image_layout":"stacked","image_size":"normal","mobile_image_style":"thumbs","color_scheme":"scheme-1","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":30}},"faq":{"type":"section-accordion","blocks":{"faq-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Does moissanite fade or change color?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>No, moissanite does not fade. In rare cases, it may show slight hints of yellow or green tones, but we carefully select high-quality stones to avoid any noticeable color changes over time.<\/p>"}},"text_wCNEX9":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Is moissanite suitable for everyday wear?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Yes, moissanite is highly durable and suitable for everyday wear. With a hardness of 9.25 on the Mohs scale, it is highly resistant to scratches and can withstand daily wear and tear.<\/p>"}},"text_MEEaGK":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Can moissanite be used for engagement rings?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Absolutely. Moissanite is a popular choice for engagement rings due to its brilliance and durability, especially for those seeking a budget-friendly alternative. Its hardness of 9.25 makes it nearly as durable as a diamond, which has a hardness of 10.<\/p>"}},"text_d7qpEX":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Will moissanite test as a diamond?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Moissanite can be detected as a diamond by standard diamond testers. However, more advanced equipment can easily distinguish between moissanite and diamonds.<\/p>"}},"text_KqkMnP":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Is moissanite hypoallergenic?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Yes, moissanite is typically set in hypoallergenic metals like 925 sterling silver or other non-reactive metals, making it suitable for most people, even those with sensitive skin.<\/p>"}},"text_t7GyjL":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Have more questions?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We’ve highlighted the 5 most common questions here, but if you have more, feel free to check out our full<a href=\"https:\/\/solariijewelry.com\/pages\/faq\" title=\"FAQ\"><em><strong>FAQ<\/strong><\/em><\/a>section for additional details.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq-1","text_wCNEX9","text_MEEaGK","text_d7qpEX","text_KqkMnP","text_t7GyjL"],"settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Moissanite Jewelry FAQ","heading_font_size":"heading-small","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-fast-shipment","icon_size":20,"width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-1","icon_color":"#545454","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_accordion_kNiVya":{"type":"section-accordion","blocks":{"icon_J7E79p":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-green-shipment","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Free shipping & Free package gifts","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p>We do our best to process and ship your order as soon as we can! Below you'll find our shipping options and their estimated shipping times.<br\/><br\/>• Free Shipping - (6-12 Business Days)<br\/>• Express Shipping - (5-8 Business Days)<br\/>• Rush Shipping - (3-5 Business Days)<\/p><p><a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}},"icon_BpFVB4":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-location","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Order tracking","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p>Tracking numbers are automatically sent once your order has been shipped. Please check your junk folder if you do not receive one 72 hours after placing your order.<\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}},"icon_D3chie":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-chat","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","title":"Contact Us","heading_font_size":"heading-small","icon_alignment":"left","text":"<p><strong>If you have any questions about your order, please reach out to us at <\/strong><a><strong>service@solariijewelry.com<\/strong><\/a><strong>. We typically respond within 24 hours.<\/strong><\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left"}}},"block_order":["icon_J7E79p","icon_BpFVB4","icon_D3chie"],"settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Shipping & Returns","heading_font_size":"heading-small","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-smile","icon_size":20,"width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-1","icon_color":"#545454","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_accordion_PCmrb3":{"type":"section-accordion","blocks":{"text_wQLh7F":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"100% Handcrafted, No Matter the Order Size","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We promise that every piece—regardless of price or quantity—is carefully handcrafted by our skilled artisans with the highest level of craftsmanship.<\/p>"}},"text_PYxhzN":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"What You See Is Exactly What You Get","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We guarantee our videos and images match the real product. No exaggeration, no surprises.<\/p>"}},"text_eNqhWM":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Hassle-Free After-Sales Support","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Enjoy 30-day easy returns, 1-year warranty, and full customer support around the clock. Shop with confidence.<\/p>"}},"text_cdMpHQ":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Eco-Friendly & Sustainable Materials","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Our pieces are made with sustainability in mind. All stones are lab-grown, and our packaging is made from biodegradable materials.<\/p>"}},"text_JNQXTT":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Premium Quality Like Works of Art","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We use only the finest materials. Every product is crafted to the highest standard—each one a wearable piece of art.<\/p>"}},"text_KVAk7C":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Free Customization on All Orders","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>We offer free customization with every product. You can request any adjustment without extra labor fees—we only charge for material upgrades if needed. No hidden costs, ever.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_wQLh7F","text_PYxhzN","text_eNqhWM","text_cdMpHQ","text_JNQXTT","text_KVAk7C"],"settings":{"default_open":false,"title":"Why Choose Us","heading_font_size":"heading-small","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-shield","icon_size":20,"width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"scheme-1","icon_color":"#545454","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_hero_Ud83fb":{"type":"section-hero","disabled":true,"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20241024-210857.gif","link":"","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","flex_align_desktop":"align--middle-center-desktop","content_width":50,"mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","flex_align_mobile":"align--middle-center-mobile","color_scheme":"","show_text_background":false,"overlay_type":"disabled","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_video_FakCBe":{"type":"section-video","name":"